Scorponok quickly pulls back behind the rock opening his left claw showing
his cyber bee inside. "How in the Slag should I know, i've only been
operational for a few megacycle. Now if youll excuse me." He fires his
cyber bee which heads straight up from the rock pillar. "I got places to
go" he yells and starts on a mad dash away, while his cyber bee opens fire
on this crazy bot.
